    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">How much does it cost to raise a child? Pick your income tier, cost of living, and number of kids to see the total cost from birth to 18, with a USDA-style category breakdown.</p>

    <div class="mb-8"><%= render "shared/ad_slot", slot: "leaderboard" %></div>

    <div data-controller="child-cost-calculator ad-engagement" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
